END, [m.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [m.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [m.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [m.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [m.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [m.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [m.ProductCategory].[LevelCate], [m.ProductCategory].[DateCreated], [m.ProductCategory].[DateModified], [m.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [m.ProductCategory].[Status], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [m.ProductCategory].[Id], [m].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [m].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [m].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [m].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [m].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [m].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [m].[Status] AS [Status0]
FROM [Products] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [m.ProductCategory] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m.ProductCategory].[Id]
WHERE [m].[Status] = 1
ORDER BY [DateCreated0] DESC

END, [m.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [m.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [m.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [m.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [m.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [m.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [m.ProductCategory].[LevelCate], [m.ProductCategory].[DateCreated], [m.ProductCategory].[DateModified], [m.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [m.ProductCategory].[Status], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [m.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [m.ProductCategory].[Id], [m].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [m].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [m].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [m].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [m].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [m].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [m].[Status] AS [Status0]
FROM [Products] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [m.ProductCategory] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m.ProductCategory].[Id]
